#
# Format:
#   # <reason for suppression>
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN
#
# Example:
#   # Disputed CVE — no actual impact in our usage of library X
#   CVE-2024-99999
#
# Review this file periodically to ensure suppressions are still valid.
